@page "/"

<PageTitle>FixFlow</PageTitle>

<section class="hero">
    <div>
        <h1>Automation for Spreadsheet-driven Trade Allocations</h1>
        <p>Configure your Spreadsheet-to-Fix parser for each counter-party to automate the extraction, normalization, transformation, validation and loading of Allocation Instructions (J) spreadsheets into compliant FIX messages. Build, validate, and deploy new mappings in minutes instead of days of custom parser work.</p>
 <!--       <div class="button-row">
            <a class="btn primary" href="direct-ingestion">Start Direct Ingestion</a>
            <a class="btn" href="map-management">Manage Mappings</a>
            <a class="btn" href="message-log">View Message Log</a>
        </div> -->
    </div>
    <div class="hero-panel">
        <div class="panel-title">Workflow Snapshot</div>
        <ol class="steps">
            <li>Create a mapping (your parser-by-configuration) for each client's trade allocation spreadsheet (CSV, XLS or XLSX)</li>
            <li>Validate your mapping by simulating your extraction, transformation and load against sample data.</li>
            <li>Use your mapping to upload allocations, preview and validate FIX output, and submit for processing.</li>
            <li>Deploy your mapping to automate allocation spreadsheet extraction from email.</li>
            <li>Monitor message logs, audit results, and export to CSV.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="grid three home-grid">
    <div class="card">
        <h2><a href="map-management">Map Management</a></h2>
        <p>Create, edit, validate, and automate FIX mapping configurations at runtime (not development time), so you can iterate custom parsers quickly, without code changes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h2><a href="direct-ingestion">Direct Ingestion</a></h2>
        <p>Upload allocation spreadsheets, validate required FIX tags, preview raw FIX output, and submit messages to FIX acceptor(s), speeding testing and reducing turnaround time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h2><a href="message-log">Full Traceability</a></h2>
        <p>Filter and review processed FIX messages, inspect statuses/errors, and export results at runtime, improving auditability and troubleshooting speed.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="grid three home-grid">
        <div class="card">
        <h2><a href="settings">Email Automation</a></h2>
        <p>Configure mailbox polling and automatically ingest allocation attachments into FIX processing at runtime, reducing manual handling and improving SLA speed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h2><a href="fix-dictionary">FIX Dictionary</a></h2>
        <p>Search tags, required fields, and valid enumerations. Message results preserve FIX dictionary order with optional sorting.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h2><a href="settings#fix-transport-parameters">Runtime Configuration</a></h2>
        <p>Edit and apply FIX transport parameters at runtime so environment fixes and routing tweaks take effect immediately without restarts, speeding iteration and reducing operational friction.</p>
    </div>
</section>
